title: Gen. Milley warns West Point graduates of 'increasing' risk of global war, 'robotic tanks' - Fox News
content: Gen. Milley warns West Point graduates of 'increasing' risk of global war, 'robotic tanks'  Fox NewsView Full Coverage on Google News
description: Gen. Mark Milley told cadets graduating from U.S. Military Academy West Point Saturday to prepare for "significant international conflict between great powers."
